node.text: Perfect Harmony hasn’t been recorded yet, we’ve been dancing to the demo our producer Alana Da Fonseca mixed for us. There’s no time on set to workshop it, so we start meeting up around town. no studio, just mads and I, our choreo team  Paul Becker // @kennyortegablog // @toricaro // @lou.sky . And our favourite hidden Phantom Ricardo Reyes (homie on the phone).. i hope you enjoy watching this as much as I do 🤞🏽 love you @themadisonreyes, and thank you @netflix for making our dream come true ❤️

node.text: LIL BRUNO GOT AN EMMY NOMINATION FOR BEST YOUNG ACTRESS 😍😍AHHHHHHHHH

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Charlie 👅🍀 on June 26, 2021 tagging @kennyortegablog. May be an image of one or more people, nature, beach, sky and ocean.

node.text: So i heard Julie had 3 Emmy wins last night.. i’ll let you in on our little secret.. it’s all due to this kook’s leadership. The man who gave us all the freedom to create in a love filled environment. Who made us want to continuously be the best versions of our characters we could possibly be, even when our only background in dancing might have been our Junior Prom(cough cough @jeremyshada). Thank you for bringing Julie & The Phantoms into so many of our lives. You are, and will always be such an inspiration to us all 🤘🏼 we love ya Kenny
